name: persona010
description:
This artwork is a part of "persona000" series. The whole project is inspired by human emotions and personality archetypes, it is my depiction of a struggle between light and dark aspects of human nature. All artwork of this series are also portraits of my soul, they've captured one unique moment of my emotional existence.

Artwork was made using mix digital technique like: digital sculpture, 3d rendering, digital painting and compositing.
size 4000x6000px
